34#ifndef OPENPAM_FEATURES_H_INCLUDED
35#define OPENPAM_FEATURES_H_INCLUDED
36
37struct openpam_feature {
38 const char *name;
39 const char *desc;
40 int onoff;
41};
42
43extern struct openpam_feature openpam_features[OPENPAM_NUM_FEATURES];
44
45/* shortcut for internal use */
46#define OPENPAM_FEATURE(f) \
47 openpam_features[OPENPAM_##f].onoff
48
49#endif
